Amazon MX Player is India's toonaangevende gratis, premium, advertentie-ondersteunde entertainmentdienst. snippet.title: Michael Is Back ‚Äì Season 2 | Official Trailer üî•
snippet.description:
Michael Is Back ‚Äì Season 2 | Official Trailer üî•

The wait is finally over! Michael is back, and the next chapter of the most intense real-life GTA series is here. After an explosive first season, the saga continues with more action, more drama, and more unpredictable real-world chaos than ever before.

Michael is back Season 2 is finally here. After a long wait, the GTA-inspired real-life series returns with bigger action, deeper drama, and higher stakes. This season follows Michael as he steps back into the chaos of the city facing old rivals, forging unexpected alliances, and pushing the limits between reality and the game. Expect cinematic car chases, intense confrontations, and heart-pounding heists that blur the line between fiction and real life.

Directed by @sidizlive

snippet.title: Saali Mohabbat | Official Trailer | ZEE5 Original | Radhika A, Divyendu S, Manish M | Pre 12th Dec
snippet.description:
A small-town housewife, Smita is devastated to find her husband and cousin dead. What happens when the local cop, Ratan, suspects her to be the one behind their murder? Watch this cat-and-mouse chase in Saali Mohabbat, premieres 12th December 2025.

Director: Tisca Chopra 
Star Cast:

Divyendu Sharma
Anurag Kashyap
Anshumaan Pushkar

The inspiration behind this video: 

Will Eleven get another chance at defeating Vecna? Is Max going to wake up? Can Will ever find peace in his life? These were just some of my biggest questions going into Stranger Things season 5, Volume 1. Seeing as it has been over three years since Stranger Things season 4's ending, my list of lingering questions has become overwhelmingly long. But I guess good things do come to those who wait, because Volume 1's four episodes quickly answer some of my most burning questions.

Set a year and a half after the events of season 4, Stranger Things season 5 finds Hawkins under military control following the "earthquake" that tore apart the town, which was actually caused by Vecna. The villain hasn't been seen since he was thrown from a window with a shotgun blast, but that hasn't stopped the group from staying ready for Vecna's next move. While Hopper and Joyce are helping Eleven train, Mike, Will, Dustin, Lucas, Nancy, Jonathan, Steve, and Robin coordinate ways to locate Vecna. Max is still present, but she remains in a coma, serving as a reminder about how high the stakes are.

Thank You So Much For Watching!

"Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is the latest romantic Bhojpuri song of 2025, released under Times Music Bhojpuri from the upcoming movie "Godfather." Sung by the dynamic duo Khesari Lal Yadav and Priyanka Singh, this love track beautifully captures the essence of romance through heartfelt lyrics and soulful melodies. With its catchy composition and visually stunning official video, this Bhojpuri DJ song is quickly becoming a fan favorite across social media and music platforms.

The music video showcases a compelling love story blending traditional Bhojpuri vibes with a modern cinematic touch. Whether you're a fan of Bhojpuri cinema, love songs, or the chart-topping voice of Khesari Lal Yadav, "Disco Mein Kisko Nachaogi" is a must-watch and a must-listen.

Presenting the second single "Ratnamala" from 'Parasakthi' starring Sivakarthikeyan, Ravi Mohan, Atharvaa, Sreeleela and others. Directed by Sudha Kongara. Music Composed by G.V. Prakash Kumar.

Lyrics: 
Pallavi 
Ratnamalaa !! Ratnamala !!  
Nannu veedi nuvvala poraadhey.  
Ratnamalaa !! Ratnamala !!  
Minnu veedi vennela poraadhey  
Ulagame suzhalvadhean? 
Udhiriyaai udaivadhean? 
yetho noolondril varaindha 
Kurippu poley tholaindheney‚Ä¶ 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Ennai vittu needhaan neengaadhey 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadhey‚Ä¶ 

Chorus 
Vaalai Kumari penne 
Vandhaan Kumaran ponne 
Solai pookkalin munne 
Olai vidu thoodhu kanne 

Chorus 
Nenjam adhu enna kallo 
Manjam ini aagum mullo 
Vanjam seyvaalo paavai 
Thanjam adhu undhan paadhai (paavai) 

Charanam 1 
Oh.. Oh.. Adiye neeyum nalamaa? 
Kadidham solli vidumaa? 
Meiyodu mutham kalandhuvaithathai 
En aasai solla vaarthai theerndhadhai‚Ä¶ 
Un pirivil nagal nogudhey 
En paruvam madal yerudhey 
Pen uruvam nizhalaanadhe 
Mei sera, maane‚Ä¶! 

Chorus 
Vaalai Kumari penne 
Vandhaan Kumaran ponne 
Solai pookkalin munne 
Olai vidu thoodhu kanne 

Chorus 
Nenjam adhu enna kallo

Vanjam seyvaalo paavai 
Thanjam adhu undhan paadhai (paavai) 

Pallavi Repeat 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadhey‚Ä¶ 

Charanam 2 
Oh.. Oh.. Azhage‚Ä¶ idhazh oram, melidhaai 
Muruval koodum 
Karum mega kootil minnal keetru pol‚Ä¶ 
Araipulli yodu neelum paattai pol‚Ä¶ 
Viral idukkin peana munai 
Idam maatru neeyum adhai‚Ä¶ 
Un meani theendidum vaira 
Madalthaalum naane‚Ä¶ 

Pallavi Final

Udhiriyaai udaivadhean? 
yetho noolondril varaindha 
Kurippu poley tholaindheney‚Ä¶ 
Ratna Malaa, Ratna Malaa 
Ennai vittu needhaan neengaadhey

Kannai vittu imaigal neengaadhey‚Ä¶

snippet.title: 4 AADMI (Official Music Video) | Sumit Parta | Mr.Maxxx | New Haryanvi Song 2025
snippet.description:
Mahra Tora presents the official music video of 4 Aadmi by Sumit Parta & Mr.Maxxx. It is a powerful Haryanvi track full of energy, emotion, and real-life hustle. 4 Aadmi celebrates confidence, struggle, and the moment when doubters finally start giving respect. It‚Äôs an anthem for every youngster chasing dreams and proving their worth through hard work.

üéß Listen to 4 Aadmi on all audio stores:-

Choro hada m bitha de chot
Bakri tu koni goat
Vair koni ghale yaar
Dekh k n kadi thoth
Jealousy na rakhu jadi
Moj me hi reu roj
Chahe khali ho ya bhari revo
Mero goj
Choro winner hai
Mehngo khave dinner hai
Part time punya kare
Full time sinner hai
Feelings inner hai
Rap game k mha
Choro jadu kre jiya witcher hai
Truth bitter hai
Log side switcher hai
Jo sath khaya piya be hi
Yaar sala snitcher hai
Dhue m uda ryo yaar sari fikar hai
Thadi mehfila me chale mero hi jikar hai
kon jle kon tle mera dhyan koni
Golibaji ala mne gyaan koni
Goli awe h chlani che bnda marwalo
Me normal banda bhgwan koni
Lagi jaat gail yaari aag dewe ge
Yaar Baniye b goli re chla dewe ge
Mehnga rakhna b howe  hatiyar lajmi
Mhari sangat me bnja khukhar admi
Re ghnta fark ni bole k ye 4 admi
Bs door rho pka me bekar admi
Khuli ankhya te hi dekhra hu bde sapne
Kad chain te tah soya mere khud yaad ni
Chiye range rover pura hangover
Nind kachi paki Chiye hot shawer
Ghadi Rm ki dhila dhila lower
Sale ve kiu chidee jo mne mile koni
mere personal kise gelya gile koni
Me to Bina dekhe mar deu  teer target pe
Ve Dhyan lake mare par pile konya
Re ghar k upar jhaj uda du
Sidha bhidle khaaj mita du
sir pe jonsa taj hta du
Satranga koi baaj bna du
Jit jit lagi lihaj mita du
Ban financer  viyaj bitha du
kisne dekhya kal re bete
Systam sara aj dikha du
